sentences: He currently has a record deal with Five Star Music.
Kcee and his longtime partner and friend hajie played as a duo for 12 years.
Their work together as music partners gave them both a few recognition until 2011 when they split, both chasing their own careers quite separately.
Kcee released "Sweet Mary J"  which was his first single in 2020.
Signed a multi millionaire endorsement deal with Tele communications company MTN in 2013
